summary:
La nostalgia está llegando.
Avengers: Endgame se ha convertido en una de las cintas más exitosas de la historia, además de...
body:
La nostalgia está llegando.

Avengers: Endgame se ha convertido en una de las cintas más exitosas de la historia, además de significar el cierre de un ciclo iniciado por Marvel Studios hace ya 11 años. Muchas historias y personajes que nos cautivaron llegaron a su punto máximos en la cinta mientras que otros están encontrando su camino hacia la grandeza.

Pero mientras eso sucede, más cintas llegan y el Universo Cinematográfico de Marvel sigue creciendo, los directores de la cinta, Joe y Anthony Russo compartieron algunas fotografías del proceso de filmación de esta gran película.

Avengers: Endgame aún está en cartelera en el mundo y se encuentra cerca de convertirse en la cinta más taquillera de todos los tiempos.

summary:
what she says: i’m fine
what she means: in avengers endgame, Rhodey briefly references Star Trek while listing off pieces of...
body:
what she says: i’m fine
what she means: in avengers endgame, Rhodey briefly references Star Trek while listing off pieces of media that cover time travel. However, the 2009 star trek movie features benedict cumberbatch in a main role. Since dr. strange is also played by cumberbatch, what implications for both universes does this bring up? Has Jim kirk seen endgame? Does he nag aos khan about it? Has tony stark seen Star Trek? If so, does 
he tease strange about it? Does benedict cumberbatch exist alongside Stephen strange? Will we ever know?

summary: Okay like there were some parts of the movie that are good but just.... They never really expand on Thanos or the main reason he...
body:
Okay like there were some parts of the movie that are good but just…. They never really expand on Thanos or the main reason he is doing this. Like in Infinity War I’m supposed to accept that him murdering Gamora is okay with no expanded background or much to go on to make him “sympathetic”.

Like I would have thought Endgame would even expand on this and why he just wants to kill half the population in the first place but instead all I get is that he is the Big Bad with some plot armor and just doing what he does because he is a villain.

In a way the whole movie was just taking down a big bully just because they are a bully.

summary: Reason why I am bawling at my computer right now: I’m typing out a story that’ll be posted Wednesday and I’m trying to come up...
body:
Reason why I am bawling at my computer right now:

  • I’m typing out a story that’ll be posted Wednesday
  • and I’m trying to come up with a title
  • Decide, “hey, this deals with Infinity War/Endgame, let’s look to the soundtracks and maybe pluck a name off of that”
  • I look for the parts of the movie that this story deals with to find a song from that point or around it
  • The titles don’t really work for what I’m going for in the story
  • See a song a few songs down and I literally TELL MYSELF “DON’T CLICK IT, YOU KNOW WHAT SCENE THAT’S FROM”
  • I click it anyway
  • Y’all…
  • I made it 4 seconds before I started bawling
  • Four
  • Gosh damn
  • Seconds
  • In conclusion: I miss Tony Stark and I’m in a constant state of jumping from denial to depression and back again in terms of my grief process
  • It has been a month and I have decided I will never get over this

summary: Disney's Aladdin Takes Off at the Memorial Day Weekend Box Office
title: Disney's Aladdin Takes Off at the Memorial Day Weekend Box Office
body:
Disney’s Aladdin Takes Off at the Memorial Day Weekend Box Office #movies #endgame #aladdin #disney

Disney’s Aladdin was the top film of the weekend box office earning an estimated $86.1 million. The film is expected to do somewhere around $105 million for the four-day weekend though some predict it’ll be over $110 million. The film received an “A” CinemaScore from opening audiences. The crowd was 54% female and 54% age 25 or older.

The film also debuted internationally in every major market…

La pellicola Marvel Studios sta bussando alla porta di Avatar e nel fine settimana del Memorial Day ha fatto un altro passo verso…
